dungeona (0.4.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Merge upstream version 019.
  * Add Tkinter GUI frontend (dungeona_gui.py) and alternate renderer
    (dungeona_ren.py).
  * Add ANSI textures for altar, grail, ogre, skeleton, floor, ceiling.
  * Add animated rat sprite frames (rat001-003.ans).
  * Add --color-mode CLI flag (256-color / 16-color grayscale).
  * Add monster pursuit AI with line-of-sight detection.
  * Add ceiling and floor texture rendering.
  * Safer curses color initialization (_safe_init_pair) for limited terminals.
  * Remove evdev gamepad dependency (dropped upstream).
  * Add python3-tk as suggested dependency for GUI frontends.
  * Update Homepage to upstream GitHub URL.
  * Ensure compatibility with Debian 13 (Trixie) and Python 3.13.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Tue, 01 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0200

